---
description: State management and persistence consistency
globs: ["src/state/**/*", "src/services/persistence/**/*", "src/domain/**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

- Keep calendar state normalized and explicit.
- Treat state as immutable: no in-place mutation.
- Validate data before state commit and before persistence write.
- Persistence adapters must be replaceable without UI changes.
- Handle corrupted persisted data safely (fallback and continue).
- Event list order should be stable and deterministic.
